rComments: She's a great teacher and she makes the class very interesting. She even shows two youtube videos each class! The tests are challenging but reasonable.

Terrible teacher.  Doesn't care if you get the notes in class.  She speaks a million words a minute.  If you ask a question she'll give you some lame theory answer that doesn't help you understand what she tries to teach.  Cognitive Pysch is something I was interested in, but she totally ruined it.

Don't understand all the negative comments (maybe from the same disgruntled student?) Class is hard cause the topic is. You can't just memorize stuff, you have to THINK. And she does a great job at making you do so.  Recommended.

So far through my college experience, this has been the worst class ever.  She makes the class harder than it has to be.  A simple concept can be turned into something where you say to yourself...wth?  And I guess there was a textbook for this class?  Yep useless again from what I heard from my classmates.  Overall, I would rather watch paint dry.
Terrible class. Each lecture ends with her telling you everything she just said is hypothetical...DO NOT TAKE, so boring

One of the worst classes I've ever taken. Professor makes material much harder than it needs to be. The book is worthless, and doesn't explain anything she talks about. She said on the first day she doesn't teach from the book, but the book should be able to be used as a reference. Don't take this class it will screw your gpa up.
Seriously don't take Psych 224 or her. You have been warned. TOO hard.
An ok professor. Recommand if you are interested in psychology. Can be a difficult class for non-psy-interested students.

I hated this class. I thought it would be semi-interesting and it turned out to be a disaster. I feel that she is a smug professor who makes the material a lot harder than it needs to be. She goes through slides very fast. She, herself, is prepared for the class, but doesn't attempt to teach in favor of the student's understanding.
better class than i thought.  she's cute but dresses like an old lady.
Don't take cognitive psych because not only is it extremely hard... but really boring as well. If you're in it... please save yourself the semester of headaches and GET OUT.
the best speaker i have had as a professor.  very prepared for each lecture and interesting to listen to.
